- Bachelor or above degree holder;
- Proven 1-2 years HR experience;
- Knowledge of HR systems and procedures, be familiar with Taiwan labor law;
- Excellent time management skills and ability to multi-task and prioritise work;
- Verbal and Written English skill;
- Strong organizational skills, team player.

